<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ881005-0025 </DOCNO><HL> Aircoa Cos. to Sell 51% Stake </HL><SO> </SO><CO> AIRC AHT </CO><IN> TNM </IN><DATELINE> DENVER  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Aircoa Cos. said it agreed in principle to sell a 51% stake to Regal Hotels International Ltd. of Hong Kong for about $51 million.    The closely held hotel management company owns an 80% stake in Aircoa Hospitality Services Inc., a hotel management concern. Aircoa Hospitality is the general partner of Aircoa Hotel Partners L.P., a real estate master limited partnership.    Aircoa Cos. said the transaction is subject to definitive agreements and regulatory approval. </TEXT></DOC>